::Reptilica/Bloodystrike/Ramulus::

Reptilica turns his head to look at Starscream. He couldn't see any reason 
why to say no.

He shruggs, nodding. "Yeah, sure, what's the news with Megatron?"
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Bloodystrike nods, silently walking over to Cave-In and picking her up. He 
glances around the group. He didn't really like Predacons, having been 
previoustly employed by the Maximals, but he didn't really dislike them 
either.

"How're you plannin' to take a hostile base with damaged troops?" he asks 
Phobia.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Ramulus' spark's repair coils finish their job, retreating back into his 
spark. Fliq was as repaired as the spark could get him, his internal repairs 
should easilly be able to take care of the rest.

Not being fully conscious, Ramulus looks over the immages from Fliq with mild 
curiosity, keeping them in his memory. He'd review them later on, right now 
he needed to get back to his body...
